# Fluff Date: 2026-03-12 17:00:46
overview:<p>Nicknamed the "Fiddler Crab" for its asymmetric silhouette, the MAD-3H is built for Abomination-heavy warfare. Four light blazers support a large laser in the right arm, providing enough combined firepower to destroy most smaller monsters. An eight-ton mace in the left arm brings any close-range fight to a savage end. Heat management requires careful use of dazzle mode when facing enemy BattleMechs.</p>

capabilities:<p>Equally dangerous at range and in melee, the Fiddler Crab demands careful threat assessment from opponents. The light blazers provide volume of fire against Abomination swarms, while the mace discourages anything from closing on the left flank. Pilots should use the large laser to engage at distance and transition to the blazers and mace as enemies close. Heat is manageable at dazzle settings but spikes rapidly at full power.</p>

